                </dd>
                <dd>
                    Integration with Cisco Finesse for the purpose of presence status retrieval using a Firefox plugin is stable
                </dd>
                <dd>
                    Call Recording/Attachment to cases has been developed but it is not 100% done
                </dd>
            </dl>
